<p>
Modern financial and legal system throughout breeds corruption, which is one of the most acute problems of global scale, as well as all kinds of injustice, lies, manipulation, fraud, and many other evils. However, in the depths of the Internet mature concepts and technologies that provide the preconditions for the construction of a new, more equitable financial and legal system. From our point is not to see how you can replace the entire system, although it is obvious how to create a new, more effective institutions, analogues of which did not exist in the past. They are not punitive, but encourage people to be honest, responsible, helpful and useful to society.
